					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 mb-4 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-100 to-teal-100 dark:from-emerald-900/30 dark:to-teal-900/30 border-2 border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-800">
						<span class="font-display font-black text-2xl text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">∞</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">面向未来</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
						培养AI时代不可替代的能力：批判性思维、创造力、协作能力和情感智慧。
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-600 dark:from-indigo-700 dark:to-violet-700 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
